                                     "actionType":  "save",
                                     "description":  {
                                                         "value":  "\u003cp\u003eThe hag chooses a creature they can see within 60 feet of them and attempts to transform them into a Beast of the hag\u0027s choice with a challenge rating of 2 or lower. The target must succeed on a DC 14 Wisdom saving throw or be transformed for 1 minute (save ends at end of turn). While transformed, the target\u0027s game statistics are replaced by the statistics of the chosen Beast, though they retain their alignment, personality, and Intelligence, Wisdom, and Charisma scores. The target\u0027s gear melds into the new form. They can\u0027t activate, use, wield, or otherwise benefit from any of their equipment. They can\u0027t speak or cast spells but can take any action the Beast can take. If the target drops to 0 hit points while in this form, they revert back to their original form with half the number of hit points they had before they transformed.\u003c/p\u003e"
